OL,3,CWatchdog investigates former PCs
OL,4,Carrested in Rotherham child sex abuse
OL,5,Cprobe
OL,7,FThe police watchdog is investigating
OL,8,Ftwo former officers who were arrested
OL,9,Ffollowing an investigation into
OL,10,Fhistoric child sex abuse.
OL,12,FThe ex-PCs were arrested last year by
OL,13,FSouth Yorkshire Police following
OL,14,Fcomplaints from four survivors of
OL,15,Fchild sexual exploitation in Rotherham
OL,16,Fin the 1990s and early 2000s.
OL,18,FSouth Yorkshire Police referred the
OL,19,Fmatter to the Independent Office for
OL,20,FPolice Conduct (IOPC) in October.
