OL,7,FIOPC director Emily Barry said: "This
OL,8,Fwas followed by more complaints from a
OL,9,Fsecond woman in November and
OL,10,Fcomplaints from two further women in
OL,11,FDecember, which were referred to us by
OL,12,FSYP as a result of their initial
OL,13,Fenquiries.
OL,15,F"Clearly these are very serious
OL,16,Fcomplaints and we will ensure they are
OL,17,Fthoroughly and robustly investigated."
