OL,7,FOne of the former officers, a retired
OL,8,Fman in his 60s, is being investigated
OL,9,Fon suspicion of abusing two girls
OL,10,Fbetween 1995 and 1999.
OL,12,FHe was arrested in October 2024 and
OL,13,Finterviewed under caution on suspicion
OL,14,Fof misconduct in public office,
OL,15,Fattempted rape and three counts of
OL,16,Findecent assault.
OL,18,FHe was further arrested this month
OL,19,Fabout reported sexual offences against
OL,20,Fa third complainant between 1997 and
OL,21,F2002 and released on bail.
