OL,5,Cprobe
OL,7,FA second former constable, aged in his
OL,8,F50s, was arrested in December on
OL,9,Fsuspicion of sexual assault and
OL,10,Fmisconduct in public office and one
OL,11,Fcount of indecent assault in
OL,12,Fconnection to incidents between 1995
OL,13,Fand 1996.
OL,15,FThe offending was reported to have
OL,16,Fhappened while the former officers,
OL,17,Fwho were both based in Rotherham, were
OL,18,Fboth on and off duty.
