OL,5,Cprobe
OL,7,FSouth Yorkshire Police Assistant Chief
OL,8,FConstable Hayley Barnett said: "We are
OL,9,Fworking closely with the Independent
OL,10,FOffice for Police Conduct to support
OL,11,Ftheir investigation, which is being
OL,12,Fcarried out by our major crime unit
OL,13,Funder the IOPC's direction and control.
OL,15,F"Together, we are committed to
OL,16,Ffollowing wherever the evidence takes
OL,17,Fus and we will take any action
OL,18,Fnecessary, as these arrests
OL,19,Fdemonstrate.
